; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests auto-xact when the amount expression returns a long (integer).
; The expression (2 * 5) returns 10 as a long, which is then converted
; to an amount. Since it has no commodity, it acts as a multiplier
; against the initial posting's amount.

= Expenses:Food
    Liabilities:Tax  (2 * 5)
    Assets:Tax       (-(2 * 5))

2024/03/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food     $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --generated
24-Mar-01 Groceries             Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-10.00            0
                                Liabilities:Tax             $100.00      $100.00
                                Assets:Tax                 $-100.00            0
end test
